  "title": "Performance Test Lead",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>Define and implement performance testing strategies, plans, and scripts.</p><p>Collaborate with architects, developers, and business stakeholders to identify performance requirements and KPIs.</p><p>Lead performance test execution, analyze results, and identify bottlenecks.</p><p>Provide detailed performance reports and recommendations to technical and business teams.</p><p>Manage performance testing tools, environments, and data.</p><p>Mentor junior testers and coordinate with global QA teams.</p><p><br /><strong>Required skills:</strong></p><p>Proven experience in performance testing and engineering</p><p><strong>Hands-on expertise with tools such as LoadRunner, JMeter, NeoLoad, or Gatling.</strong></p><p><strong>Strong scripting skills (e.g., Java, Python, JavaScript).</strong></p><p>Deep understanding of system architecture, performance tuning, and monitoring.</p><p>Excellent analytical, communication, and stakeholder management skills.</p>",
